snippet.title: PBS NewsHour full episode, Oct.19, 2020
snippet.description:
Monday on the NewsHour, with the election only 15 days away, the candidates traverse the country to appeal to voters. Plus: COVID-19 relief negotiations in Congress, what providers are seeing as the pandemic rages in the West and Midwest, caregivers in crisis, fear as a political campaign tactic, Politics Monday with Tamara Keith and Amy Walter and an essay on interracial friendships.

WATCH TODAY’S SEGMENTS
Campaigns clash over Trump’s pandemic response
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q_-zyCBsRcg
Can Congress agree on COVID-19 relief before the election?
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WOrDzYa0Srw
News Wrap: DOJ charges 6 Russians with hacking
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3gYlupBYlR4
Virus rages in rural states with limited medical resources
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v-ydRUP1QUk
A public health expert on the 'darkest part' of pandemic
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3lWcf83Ie9g
How the pandemic has pushed American caregivers into crisis
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=14koTWC5ow0
How fear-based campaigning is affecting American voters
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=55c9UHhwHBQ
Tamara Keith and Amy Walter on early voting
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KwGqONP_6fg
An essay on the importance of interracial friendships
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16g_LczFUA8

snippet.title: Best Family  Entertainment Place | Play Indoor Games For Kids | Turbo Driving Car Racing Games|
snippet.description:
Hello Friends,
I recorded this video at Arena Club Karachi also known as Arena Recreational & Sports Complex. Arena Club is located at Karsaz Karachi next to Bahria Maritime Museum Karachi people also called Navy Maritime Museum Park Karachi. 

Just to inform you that I have already uploaded detailed videos on Navy Maritime Museum Karsaz Karachi and a very good video on PAF Museum Karachi also known as PAF Museum Park here is the link of both videos for your consideration.

Maritime Museum Karachi 2020
https://youtu.be/WQ15IJb3uDo
PAF Museum Karachi 2020
https://youtu.be/s6ysHisYvnM

Now back to this video, Arena Club offers membership on yearly basis and if don't have Arena Club membership so you can get entry by purchasing ticket. The Arena Club Ticket Price 2020 is Rs. 875/- per person and children's under 3.6 feet height are free to enter inside.It has a good buffet restaurant called Arena Rangoli where you can taste variety of tasty and spicy dishes.

Arena sports club has lots of indoor games & video games for kids as well as adults. In my opinion this is the best place for physical activities for kids. You can enjoy Bowling, 8 Ball Pool, video games, 3d Virtual Video Games also it has very good ice skating area also they arrange ice skating camp for training. It has a very good Arsenal Gaming area like Chunky Money, Dolmen Mall Fun Land and like Sindbad further there is a very good video game machine where you can play car racing games like parking frenzy 2.0 3d game and other car race games.

I think this place is best for top extreme sports activities minded now a days physical activities for kids are very important. In Short it has best games under one specially Turbo Driving Car Racing Games.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/farhanjafri110
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/farhan_jafri
Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/farhanjafri

Entertaining Places / Amusement Parks / Mind Refreshing Places:
You will keep your self completely updated about the places specially in Karachi where you can take your family there in your leisure time also you will be well familiar with the places even if you visit the place 1st time.

snippet.title: Christmas Magic at Busfabriken Indoor Playground (play center fun for kids)
snippet.description:
Do you believe in Christmas magic?

Come along and watch as we enter Busfabriken lekland indoor playground in Norrköping, Sweden, at night and alone. At first, all is dark, but then…

We explore this fun play center at Christmas time and we play like we always do:

-We ride all the slides
-We jump on the trampolines
-We climb the tall wall
-We go through the spinning Star Wars tunnel
-We climb around and explore the tall jungle gym
-We ride the long tube slide

Absolutely one of our favorite indoor play areas. 

Indoor playground fun for kids and family.
